 python-zope.interface
Description: OpenFaucet - OpenFlow 1.0 library
 OpenFaucet is a Python / Twisted library implementing the OpenFlow
 1.0 protocol, used to implement controllers of OpenFlow switches.
Tag: protocol::openflow, implemented-in::python

